Join thousands of other Aramex Global Shopper members as they reap the rewards of being a Global Shopper. Just because you’re in South Africa, doesn’t mean to have to miss out on the best international deals this year. Aramex Global Shopper is a simple, secure and affordable solution that gives you access to addresses around the world to use as your own when you shop online overseas. So, how does it work? Simply shop the global online retailer of your choice and forward your parcel to any of the addresses provided to you after you sign up, and Aramex Global Shopper will ship it straight to your door in South Africa. Standard Bank and Aramex Global Shopper have partnered up to give you the best offer out there. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-375526 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aramex-High-Res-640x228.jpg" alt="Aramex-High-Res" width="640" height="228" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aramex-High-Res-640x228.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aramex-High-Res-600x213.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aramex-High-Res-768x273.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aramex-High-Res-1200x427.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aramex-High-Res.jpg 1485w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Click here to sign up for Aramex Global Shopper now. This article was published in partnership with Aramex Global Shopper.